oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Portrait, Madeline Kelly, ca. 1918-1920
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Studio portrait photograph of Madeline Kelly standing in front of a plain background. She wears a knee-length white dress with buttons down the front, tall black boots, and a hat with a large brim. She is carrying a small handbag.
